CRT.PAS is a BP7 compatible CRT unit for Win32/64 Delphi. It is a light
version of Will DeWitt's code with several bug fixes. Will's unit is
available from Code central and contains an excellent CHM help file:
http://cc.embarcadero.com/Item.aspx?id=19810

